 In this episode of the “I Said What I Said” podcast, Fk Abudu and Jola Ayeye have an insightful chat with Nicole Chikwe, founder of “The Mummy Summit”,  an amazing mother of 3 and a lovely Instagram sensation. Nicole takes us through the challenges of being a millennial mum, what parenting during the pandemic was like and how she’s able to successfully navigate it all. Listen to the podcast for all the tea!   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 